snippet.title: Pierrick Picaut
snippet.description:
My name is Pierrick, I'm a blender foundation certified trainer and CG director at Atypique Studio, a french Indie game studio.

Here you will find Blender tutorials video, focussed on intermediate and high technical level.
While I work on a lot of different things, I generaly focus on rigging and animation content in Blender 3D.
